<powerpagecomponent powerpagecomponentid="8002544a-6a5d-8ca2-e815-43196ed416a2">
  <content>{
  "copy": "&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:18PM --&gt;\n&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:12PM --&gt;\n&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:03PM --&gt;\n&lt;div class=\"row sectionBlockLayout text-start\" style=\"min-height: auto; padding: 8px;\"&gt;\n    &lt;div class=\"container\" style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap;\"&gt;\n      &lt;div class=\"col-lg-12 columnBlockLayout\" style=\"padding: 16px; margin: 60px 0px; min-height: 200px;\"&gt;\n\n        &lt;h1&gt;Developer &amp; Testing Pages&lt;/h1&gt;\n        &lt;p class=\"text-muted\"&gt;Utility pages for development, testing, and diagnostics&lt;/p&gt;\n        &lt;p class=\"text-muted\"&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;i class=\"fas fa-info-circle\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Click on any description to expand/collapse details&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n        &lt;div class=\"table-responsive mt-4\"&gt;\n          &lt;table class=\"table table-striped table-hover\"&gt;\n            &lt;thead class=\"table-dark\"&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;th style=\"width: 180px;\"&gt;Page&lt;/th&gt;\n                &lt;th&gt;Description&lt;/th&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n            &lt;/thead&gt;\n            &lt;tbody&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvcpdev\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvcpdev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Developer Testing Console&lt;/strong&gt; - Comprehensive development tool with multiple sections\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Information&lt;/strong&gt;: View current user details, roles, branch/region assignments&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Setup Query Variables&lt;/strong&gt;: Display all setup query variables (is_admin, userBranchList, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;API Calls&lt;/strong&gt;: Interactive API testing interface with multiple endpoints (Business Central OData, Dataverse, Power Pages), supports GET/POST/DELETE/PUT/PATCH methods, includes headers and POST data configuration&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JavaScript Functions&lt;/strong&gt;: Execute various utility functions (web role management, approval deletion, log operations, local storage management)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Logs&lt;/strong&gt;: Query and filter system logs with date range, user, kind, and detail filters&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commission Approvals&lt;/strong&gt;: View recent commission approval records&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Primary tool for development, debugging, and API testing.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvcpx1\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvcpx1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Data Change Detection System&lt;/strong&gt; - Hash-based monitoring tool for detecting data changes\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Calculates SHA-256 hashes of table data (branches, periods)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Compares current data against stored hashes to detect changes&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Stores hashes in browser localStorage for comparison across sessions&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Useful for monitoring when reference data tables are modified&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvcpx2\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvcpx2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Minimal Test Page&lt;/strong&gt; - Simple placeholder page\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;Displays \"X2\". Used for basic page rendering tests or as a template starting point.&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvcpx3\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvcpx3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Entity List Example&lt;/strong&gt; - Demonstrates entity list functionality\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Displays text \"X3 ex three\"&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Includes embedded entity list: \"Rodj All branch lvnCommissionBranches\"&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;Shows modern entity list with natural language search enabled&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example implementation of Power Pages entity list component.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvxcpquery\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvxcpquery&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Advanced Data Query Tool&lt;/strong&gt; - Multi-table query interface with date filtering\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Date Range Selection&lt;/strong&gt;: Quick presets (last hour, today, last 7/30 days) or custom date ranges&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multiple Tables&lt;/strong&gt;: Query logs, loan officers, commissions, or branches&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Filtering&lt;/strong&gt;: Regex-based filtering with presets to exclude/include specific users&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dynamic Schema&lt;/strong&gt;: Table headers and columns adjust based on selected table&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;API Integration&lt;/strong&gt;: Uses Power Pages Web API to fetch data dynamically&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Ideal for ad-hoc queries and data investigation across different entity types.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/lvxdata\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/lvxdata&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;User Activity Report&lt;/strong&gt; - 30-day user activity analytics and visualization\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary Statistics&lt;/strong&gt;: Total log entries, unique users, average daily activity, most active day&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Daily Breakdown&lt;/strong&gt;: Table view with activity bars showing logs per day&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Filtering&lt;/strong&gt;: Toggle to exclude/include test and admin users (default excludes Loanvisiontesting, Robert Martin, Michael LeBuhn)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;View Modes&lt;/strong&gt;: Table view (default) or chart view&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Server-Side Data&lt;/strong&gt;: Uses FetchXML to query last 30 days of logs, processes client-side for flexibility&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Comprehensive activity reporting for understanding portal usage patterns.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/diag\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/diag&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;System Diagnostics &amp; Data Browser&lt;/strong&gt; - Comprehensive system information and data inspection tool\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Current User Information&lt;/strong&gt;: Complete user profile, roles, branch/loan officer assignments&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Period Data&lt;/strong&gt;: Full period table with all fields (period number, dates, visibility, codes)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Branch Data&lt;/strong&gt;: Complete branch listing with codes, names, and metadata&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Loan Officer Data&lt;/strong&gt;: Full loan officer table with assignments and details&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Commission Summary&lt;/strong&gt;: Aggregated commission totals by loan officer, branch, and type&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Setup Variables&lt;/strong&gt;: All system configuration variables and user-specific settings&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Primary tool for inspecting system data, verifying configurations, and troubleshooting data-related issues.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n              &lt;tr&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;&lt;a href=\"/_services/about\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;/_services/about&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\n                &lt;td&gt;\n                  &lt;div class=\"page-description\"&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-header\" onclick=\"toggleDescription(this)\"&gt;\n                      &lt;strong&gt;Power Pages System Diagnostics&lt;/strong&gt; - Built-in Microsoft portal information page\n                      &lt;i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down float-end\"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                    &lt;div class=\"description-details\" style=\"display: none;\"&gt;\n                      &lt;ul class=\"mb-0 mt-2\"&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portal Details&lt;/strong&gt;: Version, build number, Portal ID, Organization ID, Tenant ID&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Geographic Region&lt;/strong&gt;: Shows deployment region (e.g., NAM for North America)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portal Type&lt;/strong&gt;: Template information (e.g., PowerPages_BlankTemplate_V2)&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Auth Key Expiration&lt;/strong&gt;: Date when portal authentication key needs renewal&lt;/li&gt;\n                        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cache Management Tools&lt;/strong&gt;: Buttons to clear portal cache or config cache (useful for troubleshooting)&lt;/li&gt;\n                      &lt;/ul&gt;\n                      &lt;p class=\"mb-0 mt-2 text-muted\"&gt;&lt;em&gt;Essential for support tickets, troubleshooting, and verifying portal configuration.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n                    &lt;/div&gt;\n                  &lt;/div&gt;\n                &lt;/td&gt;\n              &lt;/tr&gt;\n            &lt;/tbody&gt;\n          &lt;/table&gt;\n        &lt;/div&gt;\n\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;style&gt;\n.table th {\n  vertical-align: middle;\n}\n\n.table td {\n  vertical-align: top;\n}\n\n.table a {\n  font-family: monospace;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  font-size: 0.95em;\n}\n\n.alert ul {\n  padding-left: 20px;\n}\n\nul li {\n  margin-bottom: 4px;\n}\n\n.description-header {\n  cursor: pointer;\n  padding: 4px 0;\n  user-select: none;\n}\n\n.description-header:hover {\n  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);\n}\n\n.description-header i {\n  transition: transform 0.2s ease;\n  font-size: 0.8em;\n  margin-top: 4px;\n}\n\n.description-header.expanded i {\n  transform: rotate(180deg);\n}\n\n.description-details {\n  overflow: hidden;\n  transition: max-height 0.3s ease;\n}\n&lt;/style&gt;\n\n&lt;script&gt;\nfunction toggleDescription(header) {\n  const details = header.nextElementSibling;\n  const icon = header.querySelector('i');\n\n  if (details.style.display === 'none') {\n    details.style.display = 'block';\n    header.classList.add('expanded');\n  } else {\n    details.style.display = 'none';\n    header.classList.remove('expanded');\n  }\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:03PM --&gt;\n&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:12PM --&gt;\n&lt;!-- Last modified Tue Oct 21 3:18PM --&gt;",
